</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>
<placeName>鄜州</placeName>都督尉遲敬德表乞骸骨<pc>；</pc>
<num value="42">乙巳</num>
<pc>，</pc>以敬德為開府儀同<num value="3">三</num>司<pc>，</pc>
<measure quantity="5" unit="days">
<num value="5">五</num>日</measure>
<num value="1">一</num>參<pc>。</pc>
