<quote>王兄弟既多<pc>，</pc>陛下<num value="1000">千</num>秋<measure quantity="10000" unit="years">
<num value="10000">萬</num>歲</measure>後<pc>，</pc>宜得壯士以自衛<pc>。</pc>
